com.streambase.sbunit.ext.matcher.builder

Class CSVMatcherBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.streambase.sbunit.ext.matcher.builder.CSVMatcherBuilder

  • public class CSVMatcherBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    Build matchers to match a subset of a tuple's fields from CSV strings. Any fields that aren't mentioned in the constructor are ignored.

      • makeMatcher

        public FieldBasedTupleMatcher makeMatcher(java.lang.String csvText)
                                   throws com.streambase.sb.StreamBaseException
        Build a matcher from this CSV text that matches only the fields given to the constructor. Note that an empty column is null, e.g. "hi,,there" has null for the 2nd column. The corresponding field in the matched tuple must be null.
        Returns:
        The Matcher for this CSV row.
        Throws:
        com.streambase.sb.StreamBaseException

      • makeMatcher

        public FieldBasedTupleMatcher makeMatcher(java.lang.String... columns)
                                   throws com.streambase.sb.StreamBaseException
        Build a matcher from string values that matches only the fields given to the constructor. Note that either a null column or an empty string matches a null field
        Parameters:
        columns - String value for each column matching the field names in the constructor
        Returns:
        The Matcher for this CSV row.
        Throws:
        com.streambase.sb.StreamBaseException
